  "texts": [
    "Additionally, to the best of our knowledge, this study is a pioneering endeavor in the field of endodontics utilizing the PDF add-on.The accuracy threshold for AI applications in clinical decision-making processes is generally accepted to be at least 90% to ensure patient safety and clinical effectiveness [28,29].",
    "In this study, responses from the chatbots were categorized as \"insufficient\" if they were not completely correct or incorrect according to the AAE's RET guidelines [23].",
    "While evaluating the results of our study, PDF-enabled ChatGPT-4 surpassed the accuracy threshold with a correct response rate of 98.1%, showing the best performance among the evaluated applications, while Gemini provided the most incorrect responses symbolizing the lowest accuracy.",
    "Remarkably, PDF-enabled ChatGPT-4 produced no incorrect responses, and only one answer was considered \"insufficient. \"",
    "Based on these findings, the H1 hypothesis of the study was accepted."
  ],
